  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "A stream of deadly Q-Viruses is taking over the universe by exterminating any sign of life that gets in the way! There's only one way to save civilization-crack the Q-Virus' DNA Code and obliterate them all. In \"Double Sequence,\" players shift and slide blocks of the random genetic code in order to match like colors. This will not be easy-the patterns become more difficult as the Q-Virus ravaged more planets.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
